We are pleased to announce that we have appointed Michael Brown as Chief
Operating Officer of Enron Europe.

Michael joined Enron,s London legal department in 1995 and has played a key
role in the success of many of our large commercial ventures since then.  In
July 1999, he was made Enron Europe,s General Counsel.  Replacing Michael in
the General Counsel role will be Mark Evans who joined our legal department
in 1995.

Please join us in congratulating Michael and Mark in their new roles.